Package org.eclipse.rdf4j.console Description

A command line console tool for querying and updating local or remote RDF4J repositories.

Usage: 

java org.openrdf.console.Console [option] [repository-id]

Use 

-h
or 
--help
to get the list of available options and their respective arguments. See also the RDF4J console documentation for additional information on using this tool.
